# macOS-native priorities (v1)

## Capture

- Use **ScreenCaptureKit** for system audio capture.
- Treat permission failures as first-class UX: explain what to enable and why.
- Always record to disk in parallel with any rolling chunk pipeline.

## Audio

- Expect capture audio to arrive as sample buffers; convert with **AVFoundation**.
- Normalize pipeline: 48k stereo → 16k mono (or whatever WhisperKit expects).

## Packaging

- Prefer native app bundle behaviors (sandbox, file access, entitlement planning).
- Don’t add Electron/Tauri/RN layers for v1.

